message.content: It is difficult to generalize an entire generation of kids in Bolivia as being obsessed with a specific thing. However, like many other countries, kids in Bolivia may exhibit a range of interests and obsessions. Some common obsessions seen among kids in Bolivia, as well as globally, could include technology, video games, social media platforms, music, fashion trends, sports, and celebrities. However, it is important to note that interests and obsessions can vary greatly among individuals, and not all kids would necessarily be obsessed with the same things.
